                <h1>Hoof &#039;n&#039; Horn opens Triangle premiere of &#039;American Idiot&#039; this weekend</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/b8893007-3faf-4f09-ac25-3579f83a47e1.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/tim-campbell">Tim Campbell</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">April 14, 2016 | 2:59am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
